Subject: Migrate From Netwrix Auditor to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor
Description:
Migrate From Netwrix Auditor to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor

Hello Team,

We currently have Netwrix Auditor and would like to stand up a new Server with the current Netwrix Auditor we have plus Sharepoint auditing.

Is there any chance someone can arrange a meeting with me and I can show you what we have on our current Netwrix environment and I can go ahead and stand up new servers and so forth.

Thank you
What_We_Know__c:
The customer wants to migrate from Netwrix Auditor to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor. They want to do the configurations themselves but they dont want to engage Professional Support team.

Alex Buchta engaged the account manager and Professional Services team to move ahead with the installation phase.
Next_Steps__c: Closing ticket as customer has been reached out to by Account Manager to connect them with PSO team.
Solution_Comment__c: I was just informed that Marti has reached out to Customer for discussing available timeslots to move ahead with Netwrix Enterprise Auditor installation and onboarding process with the Professional Services tea
